ğŸ”§ Smart Contract Architecture
1. ContentVault.sol
Manages content access control and paywall logic.
Key Functions:

createContent(uint256 price, string uri) - Create paywalled content
purchaseAccess(uint256 contentId) - Buy content with MNEE
hasAccess(address user, uint256 contentId) - Check access rights

2. RevenueStreamer.sol
Handles subscription billing and automated renewals.
Key Functions:

createSubscription(uint256 price, uint256 duration) - Set up subscription tier
subscribe(uint256 subId) - Subscribe with MNEE approval
renewSubscription(uint256 subId) - Auto-renew logic

3. SplitPayment.sol
Executes programmable revenue distribution.
Key Functions:

setSplit(address[] recipients, uint256[] percentages) - Configure splits
distributePayment(uint256 amount) - Execute MNEE distribution
withdrawShare() - Claim accumulated MNEE


