ğŸ¯ How MNEE is Used
VaultLink integrates MNEE (0x8ccedbAe4916b79da7F3F612EfB2EB93A2bFD6cF) as the primary payment currency:

Paywall Payments: Users pay MNEE to unlock content
Subscriptions: Monthly/annual billing in MNEE with auto-renewal
Revenue Splits: Smart contracts distribute MNEE to multiple creators
Instant Payouts: Creators receive MNEE directly to their wallets
Analytics: All revenue tracking in stable USD-equivalent MNEE
Why MNEE?


âœ… USD-backed stability (no crypto volatility)
âœ… ERC-20 standard (seamless integration)
âœ… Ethereum mainnet (security & decentralization)
âœ… Programmable (smart contract automation)


